comments: I noticed that sometimes color of the object was associated with one half of the word. I didn't use any strategies, I just learned it as normal. I didn't use paper to make notes, because it would be cheating and also I didn't have time. Easy was the training part and a little bit harder was part with the partner, because I think we learned the same, but a little different languages. I was learned that zeticoe was for every color of the "star", but my partner had different spelling for every color.
